176
00:08:59,359 --> 00:09:01,317
Actually, you know what? I'm fine!

177
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,109
So maybe we should just turn around.

178
00:09:03,192 --> 00:09:04,734
A student, here? Now?

179
00:09:04,817 --> 00:09:06,525
I can't have her seeing us together.

180
00:09:06,609 --> 00:09:09,734
