214
00:10:22,109 --> 00:10:23,859
And wouldn't ya know it, there's a student here, too!

215
00:10:23,942 --> 00:10:25,234
What are the chances of seeing two people

216
00:10:25,317 --> 00:10:26,859
from the school in the exact same place!

217
00:10:26,942 --> 00:10:28,150
Hm? What was your name?

218
00:10:28,234 --> 00:10:29,650
It's Aioi, isn't that right?

219
00:10:29,734 --> 00:10:31,567
