236
00:11:39,484 --> 00:11:41,359
After one whole month of investigating,

237
00:11:41,442 --> 00:11:43,109
I've determined that Nano Shinonome

238
00:11:43,192 --> 00:11:46,234
visits the supermarket in this district every Saturday.

239
00:11:46,317 --> 00:11:49,192
If my calculations are correct, she'll be arriving soon.

240
00:11:49,275 --> 00:11:51,859
And once she does, I'll be right behind her.

241
00:11:51,942 --> 00:11:53,234
When I find my opening,

242
00:11:53,317 --> 00:11:55,942
I'll call upon my trusty friend, Mr. Short Circuit,

243
00:11:56,025 --> 00:11:58,192
